public class AccountImpl
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements java.io.Serializable, Account

Account class that represents a simple bank account Subclasses UnicastRemoteObject because Accounts are passed between the ATMImplementation and Bank remote objects. 12/8/2011
